6:
That was very impressive, Roselia,
but I must emphasize... We do NOT
use the window to enter the
cafeteria!
10:
Huh? But I saw others fly in through
the window before!
12:
That's because they have wings.
Last I checked, you don't.
15:
Haha... True. My bad, my bad!
I'm just not really getting these
"safety measures" people keep
going on about.
19:
You need to work on adjusting to a
peaceful life. Why don't you try
doing something normal? Like...
shopping, for example?
24:
Shopping!
I like the sound of that!
27:
Excellent. It's decided, then.
I know several good shops around
Palpebra you could—
32:
Actually, my world has TONS of
great stores as well. I'd like to take
Stella to see them!
38:
W-wait a minute. If you go back to
your world, the pirates will go after
you!
Did you forget that already?!
42:
Look here, Stella! Isn't the handiwork
on this coral incredible?
49: I told you my world was great!
53:
Well, it looks like they're having a
good time.
57:
You coming, I can understand. But
why the hell was I dragged along?! I
don't know anythin' about fashion.
61:
Shopping is hard work, Nimbus! The
more people to carry bags, the
better!
67:
Carry... bags? What am I, your
manservant or something?!
71:
What's up, Stella? Found something
that caught your eye?
75:
Roselia... You really like fashion, don't
you?
78:
I mean, yeah! It makes me happy,
what can I say?
81:
We could die at any moment, right?
When I wake up tomorrow,
something unexpected could
happen and BAM—no more Roselia.
82:
Here's what I figure... If we're gonna
die one day, why not die doing what
we love?
86:
Luckily, today I'm surrounded by the
things I love: fashion, and my
friends!
Even if I were to die right now, I'd at
least die happy!
89:
I see.
However... Please don't die, Roselia.
91:
Okie-dokie!
I'll make sure to be extra careful
today!
94:
As a thanks for coming out with me
today, I want to give each of you
one thing you want!
96:
Alk and Stella, why don't you two go
pick out something together?
101:
Okay!
Wait a minute, is Nimbus not
included in this?
105:
Whatever. I don't need to play dress
up.
You two get goin' and pick out your
fancy clothes.
111:
You haven't forgotten that whole
business with the pirates, have you?
116:
But this area is under the jurisdiction
of the Gaean Navy. We won't be
running into pirates here. Most likely.
120:
I don't like the sound of that "most
likely".
122:
Listen here. I know you don't much
value your life. But when it comes to
other people, you need to be careful.
124:
If you're gonna get yourself killed,
make sure you don't bring others
down with you.
Your death wish is yours alone.
129:
You're right... I'm sorry.
I'll make sure to remember that.
133:
Unfortunately, keeping others from
getting hurt because of you is...
easier said than done.
138:
Have you two decided what you
want?
142:
Not yet—actually, we wanted to talk
to you about something!
156: Yes. I think it would be fun.
163:
That does sound fun! Let's do it!
Right now!
168:
Oh, now? We were thinking about
doing it like... a week from now.
175:
I mean, there's no need to rush. It'd
be better to take our time choosing
a gift, don't you think?
179:
I... suppose.
A week is a long time, though...
182:
Oh I can hardly wait!
I can't remember the last time I felt
this excited about something!
184:
All right, one week—promise you
won't forget!
187: Cross your heart and hope to die!
